- Add sync_nf_probe_expected_sha.sh to align wrangler var + CF secret
- Use pin (not git HEAD) for platform checks in nf_post_deploy_verify
- Add GHA workflow to sync + redeploy probe worker on dispatch/push
- Set EXPECTED_GIT_SHA in wrangler.toml to live e0bb318c9ef8
